00:24:02,790 --> 00:24:05,320
What do you think of this complete version of Magical Destroy?

404
00:24:05,320 --> 00:24:08,360
Um, I don't see much of a difference from before.

405
00:24:08,360 --> 00:24:14,130
What? I went and edited it to target the audience for the general public, and yet you still don't understand?

406
00:24:14,130 --> 00:24:17,170
Then I'll use the ultimate way to explain this as easily as possible!

